summary: so they’ve said they won’t have Ciri or a Gwent-style minigame in Cyberpunk 2077, and i respect that but hear me out DLC, right?...
body:
so they’ve said they won’t have Ciri or a Gwent-style minigame in Cyberpunk 2077, and i respect that but hear me out

DLC, right? V hears from a friend of a friend that a girl with white hair and no implants (huh, weird) taught her how to play this nifty card game, and it’s starting to catch on with ripper docs, landlords, shopowners…

but enough beating around the bush; Ciri teaches the people who harbor her how to play Gwent, they make new Night City-appropriate factions, and the game gets popular with certain people
